Class DockablePreferencesManager<D>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drombler.commons.docking.impl.DockablePreferencesManager<D>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - the Dockable type

    public class DockablePreferencesManager<D>
extends Object
    A manager to manage the DockablePreferences. Note: This class is some pre-work for changing (once drag'n'drop is supported) DockablePreferences. TODO: Thread-safe?

    puce
